{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2021-08/Additional-properties-that-influence-positioning/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"好成的blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f715fd2a-f251-5258-ac24-ec00fb9811fa","excerpt":"现在我们已经讨论了盒子模型的属性在不同的元素类型中是如何变化的，让我们来看看影响盒子模型定位的几个额外的属性。 ：影响相邻边距，仅应用两个边距中较大的一个。 :负值的边距用于定位内容。 :当容器框内的内容大于其父级或设置的偏移量超过父级盒子，它会溢出。控制如何处理。 :可以使用 max-width、max-height…","html":"<p>现在我们已经讨论了盒子模型的属性在不同的元素类型中是如何变化的，让我们来看看影响盒子模型定位的几个额外的属性。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Margin collapsing</code>：影响相邻边距，仅应用两个边距中较大的一个。</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Negative margins</code>:负值的边距用于定位内容。</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Overflow</code>:当容器框内的内容大于其父级或设置的偏移量超过父级盒子，它会溢出。<code class=\"language-text\">overflow</code>控制如何处理。</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">max-width, max-height, min-width, min-height</code>:可以使用 max-width、max-height、min-width 和 min-height 属性进一步限制宽度和高度。</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Pseudo-elements</code>:允许在从 CSS 选择的元素中生成额外的元素。它们通常用于为布局生成附加内容或提供特定的视觉外观。</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Stacking contexts and rendering order</code>:决定了 z 轴方向的渲染。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Margin collapsing</h3>\n<p>边距塌陷：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>大吃小，相等的保留一个。</li>\n<li>只有竖直方向的 margin 会 collapse，水平方向的 margin 从来不会。</li>\n<li>只有 block-level 的元素可以 collapse，floats，absolutely 和 inline-block 元素永远不会 collapse。inline-level 元素没有 margin(竖直方向上)，所以也不会 collapse。</li>\n<li>只有参与相同的 BFC 的盒子才会 collapse(Note that block formatting contexts are not established by block boxes with overflow: visible (the default value))。</li>\n<li>只有相邻的 margin 才会发生 collapse。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>把盒子的 margin 当作盒子自己的。有以下情况会发生相邻：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>父和子的 margin</li>\n<li>相邻盒子的 margin</li>\n<li>爷与父与子</li>\n<li>没有内容的元素的 margin</li>\n</ul>\n<p>被以下分离的 margin 不会 collapse：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>content(e.g.text)</li>\n<li>padding or border（例如，如果父级有填充或边框，则其边距不能与其子项的边距折叠，否则它们会折叠）</li>\n<li>清除（例如清除浮动的结果可能会将边距分开，以至于它们不会折叠。）</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">.m {\r\n  margin: 10px;\r\n  background-color: #fb9a99;\r\n}\r\n.parent {\r\n  margin: 10px;\r\n  background-color: #a6cee3;\r\n}\r\nbody {\r\n  background-color: #b2df8a;\r\n}\r\n&lt;div class=\"parent\">\r\n  &lt;div class=\"m\">Hello world&lt;/div>\r\n  &lt;div class=\"m\">Hello world&lt;/div>\r\n  &lt;div class=\"m\">Hello world&lt;/div>\r\n&lt;/div></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b56c50aa046d1f52b1396899e9e98b52/07f3a/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 27.848101265822784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"margin\"\n        title=\"margin\"\n        src=\"/static/b56c50aa046d1f52b1396899e9e98b52/828fb/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b56c50aa046d1f52b1396899e9e98b52/ff44c/1.jpg 158w,\n/static/b56c50aa046d1f52b1396899e9e98b52/a6688/1.jpg 315w,\n/static/b56c50aa046d1f52b1396899e9e98b52/828fb/1.jpg 630w,\n/static/b56c50aa046d1f52b1396899e9e98b52/07f3a/1.jpg 740w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">.m {\r\n  overflow: auto;\r\n  margin: 10px;\r\n  background-color: #fb9a99;\r\n}\r\n.parent {\r\n  overflow: auto;\r\n  margin: 10px;\r\n  background-color: #a6cee3;\r\n}\r\nbody {\r\n  overflow: auto;\r\n  background-color: #b2df8a;\r\n}\r\n&lt;div class=\"parent\">\r\n  &lt;div class=\"m\">Hello world&lt;/div>\r\n  &lt;div class=\"m\">Hello world&lt;/div>\r\n  &lt;div class=\"m\">Hello world&lt;/div>\r\n&lt;/div></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/47cbc89ab748f2355f999cc92b3841e3/97cfc/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 27.848101265822784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/47cbc89ab748f2355f999cc92b3841e3/828fb/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/47cbc89ab748f2355f999cc92b3841e3/ff44c/2.jpg 158w,\n/static/47cbc89ab748f2355f999cc92b3841e3/a6688/2.jpg 315w,\n/static/47cbc89ab748f2355f999cc92b3841e3/828fb/2.jpg 630w,\n/static/47cbc89ab748f2355f999cc92b3841e3/97cfc/2.jpg 736w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">.m {\r\n  margin: 10px;\r\n  background-color: #fb9a99;\r\n  border: 3px solid #e31a1c;\r\n}\r\n.parent {\r\n  margin: 10px;\r\n  background-color: #a6cee3;\r\n  border: 3px solid #1f78b4;\r\n}\r\nbody {\r\n  background-color: #b2df8a;\r\n  border: 3px solid #33a02c;\r\n}\r\n&lt;div class=\"parent\">\r\n  &lt;div class=\"m\">Hello world&lt;/div>\r\n  &lt;div class=\"m\">Hello world&lt;/div>\r\n  &lt;div class=\"m\">Hello world&lt;/div>\r\n&lt;/div></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0408182405cf757773c55c1dcdb5cb31/49b61/3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 26.58227848101266%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"3\"\n        src=\"/static/0408182405cf757773c55c1dcdb5cb31/828fb/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0408182405cf757773c55c1dcdb5cb31/ff44c/3.jpg 158w,\n/static/0408182405cf757773c55c1dcdb5cb31/a6688/3.jpg 315w,\n/static/0408182405cf757773c55c1dcdb5cb31/828fb/3.jpg 630w,\n/static/0408182405cf757773c55c1dcdb5cb31/49b61/3.jpg 752w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>负的 margin</h3>\n<p>最好不要用，会发生重叠(overlap)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">.negative {\r\n  margin-top: -2em\r\n  ;\r\n  margin-left: 30px;\r\n}\r\n&lt;div class=\"blue\">In the case of negative margins, the maximum of the absolute values of the negative adjoining margins is deducted from the maximum of the positive adjoining margins.&lt;/div>\r\n&lt;div class=\"negative\">If there are no positive margins, the maximum of the absolute values of the adjoining margins is deducted from zero.&lt;/div></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/096d198b14342422fa0af551a5bf34e5/72747/4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 17.72151898734177%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/static/096d198b14342422fa0af551a5bf34e5/828fb/4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/096d198b14342422fa0af551a5bf34e5/ff44c/4.jpg 158w,\n/static/096d198b14342422fa0af551a5bf34e5/a6688/4.jpg 315w,\n/static/096d198b14342422fa0af551a5bf34e5/828fb/4.jpg 630w,\n/static/096d198b14342422fa0af551a5bf34e5/72747/4.jpg 764w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>overflow</h3>\n<p>默认值 visible，然和超过 visible 的值，不适用于 display: inline 元素，然后不是 visible 的值都将创建一个新的 BFC。</p>\n<h3>max-width, max-height, min-width and min-height</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>max- / min-width</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>&#x3C; length ></td>\n<td>指定固定的最小或最大使用宽度。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&#x3C; percentage ></td>\n<td>指定一个百分比来确定使用的值。该百分比是相对于生成的方框的包含块的宽度计算的。如果包含区块的宽度为负数，则使用值为零。如果包含区块的宽度取决于这个元素的宽度，那么产生的布局在 CSS2.1 中是未定义的。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>none</td>\n<td>（仅适用于 ‘max-width’）框的宽度没有限制。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>max- / min-height</strong></td>\n<td><strong>Description</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&#x3C; length ></td>\n<td>指定固定的最小或最大使用宽度。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&#x3C; percentage ></td>\n<td>指定一个百分比来确定使用的值。这个百分比是相对于生成的盒子的包含块的高度计算的。如果没有明确指定包含块的高度（即取决于内容高度），并且该元素没有绝对定位，百分比值将被视为 “0”（对于 “最小高度”）或 “无”（对于 “最大高度”）。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>none</td>\n<td>（仅适用于 ‘max-height’）框的高度没有限制。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>值得注意的是：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">html, body {\r\n  height: 100%;\r\n}\r\n.height {\r\n  height: 100%;\r\n}\r\n&lt;div class=\"height blue\">\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aliquam at orci ac libero euismod mollis et porta elit. Proin a ultricies turpis. Nam tortor risus, sodales non ultrices ac, interdum sed dui. Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Nunc at mollis elit. Proin at molestie diam. In ultrices erat nec ante eleifend, quis vestibulum ante elementum. Phasellus nec dapibus urna, ut sodales felis. Quisque dolor lectus, tincidunt vel augue ut, feugiat porttitor purus.\r\n\r\nPraesent commodo blandit lacinia. Etiam mollis rutrum enim, non congue tortor semper in. Donec commodo metus id turpis dapibus, ut ultricies ante porta. Sed cursus dignissim eros cursus ullamcorper. Curabitur eleifend, turpis commodo tempus convallis, diam orci consequat velit, eu auctor mi felis eu elit. Sed lectus ipsum, hendrerit id dui eu, imperdiet dictum eros. Nullam tincidunt dignissim felis sit amet blandit.\r\n&lt;/div></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a431f0fcf5e255d736248f8e51dcddb7/63ec5/6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 16.455696202531648%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"6\"\n        title=\"6\"\n        src=\"/static/a431f0fcf5e255d736248f8e51dcddb7/f058b/6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a431f0fcf5e255d736248f8e51dcddb7/c26ae/6.png 158w,\n/static/a431f0fcf5e255d736248f8e51dcddb7/6bdcf/6.png 315w,\n/static/a431f0fcf5e255d736248f8e51dcddb7/f058b/6.png 630w,\n/static/a431f0fcf5e255d736248f8e51dcddb7/63ec5/6.png 812w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\r\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ae36b588e2f2ed6ad137f63c87a64752/31aff/7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 17.72151898734177%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"7\"\n        title=\"7\"\n        src=\"/static/ae36b588e2f2ed6ad137f63c87a64752/f058b/7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ae36b588e2f2ed6ad137f63c87a64752/c26ae/7.png 158w,\n/static/ae36b588e2f2ed6ad137f63c87a64752/6bdcf/7.png 315w,\n/static/ae36b588e2f2ed6ad137f63c87a64752/f058b/7.png 630w,\n/static/ae36b588e2f2ed6ad137f63c87a64752/31aff/7.png 823w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">html, body {\r\n  height: 100%;\r\n}\r\n.min-height {\r\n  min-height: 100%;\r\n}\r\n&lt;div class=\"min-height blue\">\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aliquam at orci ac libero euismod mollis et porta elit. Proin a ultricies turpis. Nam tortor risus, sodales non ultrices ac, interdum sed dui. Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Nunc at mollis elit. Proin at molestie diam. In ultrices erat nec ante eleifend, quis vestibulum ante elementum. Phasellus nec dapibus urna, ut sodales felis. Quisque dolor lectus, tincidunt vel augue ut, feugiat porttitor purus.\r\n\r\nPraesent commodo blandit lacinia. Etiam mollis rutrum enim, non congue tortor semper in. Donec commodo metus id turpis dapibus, ut ultricies ante porta. Sed cursus dignissim eros cursus ullamcorper. Curabitur eleifend, turpis commodo tempus convallis, diam orci consequat velit, eu auctor mi felis eu elit. Sed lectus ipsum, hendrerit id dui eu, imperdiet dictum eros. Nullam tincidunt dignissim felis sit amet blandit.\r\n&lt;/div></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e99ba2a0acbfae5e26b02aef595295ae/f0685/8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25.316455696202528%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"8\"\n        title=\"8\"\n        src=\"/static/e99ba2a0acbfae5e26b02aef595295ae/f058b/8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e99ba2a0acbfae5e26b02aef595295ae/c26ae/8.png 158w,\n/static/e99ba2a0acbfae5e26b02aef595295ae/6bdcf/8.png 315w,\n/static/e99ba2a0acbfae5e26b02aef595295ae/f058b/8.png 630w,\n/static/e99ba2a0acbfae5e26b02aef595295ae/f0685/8.png 835w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\r\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9f3e70754d972e5e081401026ea5e640/a1dd2/9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25.949367088607595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"9\"\n        title=\"9\"\n        src=\"/static/9f3e70754d972e5e081401026ea5e640/f058b/9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9f3e70754d972e5e081401026ea5e640/c26ae/9.png 158w,\n/static/9f3e70754d972e5e081401026ea5e640/6bdcf/9.png 315w,\n/static/9f3e70754d972e5e081401026ea5e640/f058b/9.png 630w,\n/static/9f3e70754d972e5e081401026ea5e640/a1dd2/9.png 838w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>第一种情况设置的是 height：100%，这种情况只是将盒子高度设置成父元素的高度在这个例子中是 body 的高度，文本太长，发生了溢出。\r\n第二种情况设置的是 min-height：100%，这种情况如果发生了溢出，会触发 height：auto,block-level 元素就是 content-based，所以盒子的高度始终装得下文本，不管 body 的大小。但是如果文本太少的话，不会触发 auto，只是将高度设为父元素的高度。</p>\n<h3>Pseudo-elements</h3>\n<p>伪元素生成的内容放置在元素<strong>内部</strong>，在元素内容的开头或结尾：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">.example:before {\r\n  content: 'Hello ';\r\n}\r\n.example:after {\r\n  content: '!!!';\r\n}\r\n&lt;p class=\"example blue\">world&lt;/p></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 622px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c6b95e2d4a3999701386b9bafcac458f/604ec/10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.025316455696203%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAIAAADXZGvcAAAACXBIWXMAABJNAAASTQHzl8SnAAAAR0lEQVQI12M4f+vR1jO39lx+sPPC3QM3nh26/ZIYdPDWizMP3jCcvvl47YkbOy4+2Hz29p7rz/fferP/1muCaO/NVyfvvwMAwFtkAEeovesAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"10\"\n        title=\"10\"\n        src=\"/static/c6b95e2d4a3999701386b9bafcac458f/604ec/10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c6b95e2d4a3999701386b9bafcac458f/c26ae/10.png 158w,\n/static/c6b95e2d4a3999701386b9bafcac458f/6bdcf/10.png 315w,\n/static/c6b95e2d4a3999701386b9bafcac458f/604ec/10.png 622w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 622px) 100vw, 622px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Stacking contexts and z-index</h3>\n<p>具有负 z-index 的元素绘制在 normal flow 和 floats 下方，具有正 x-index 的元素绘制在 normal flow 和 floats 上方。 如果两个元素具有相同的 z-index，则它们会根据它们在 HTML 标记中的顺序从后到前堆叠。\r\n请注意，只有定位(relative 或者 absolute)元素可以具有 z-index，例如为 normal flow blocks or floats 设置 z-index 不会影响它们的渲染顺序。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Additional properties that influence positioning","date":"August 16, 2021","description":"学习CSS布局(3)"},"timeToRead":7},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2021-08/Box sizing in CSS/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Box sizing in CSS"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2021-08/CSS3-flexbox/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS3:Flexbox"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"f715fd2a-f251-5258-ac24-ec00fb9811fa","previousPostId":"b72a5eec-3d5c-5906-9c32-a0c8ba415091","nextPostId":"b5020d1d-a4f6-5f80-9952-4f4bdffd94ea"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3415673938"]}